            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-05-14</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Improved custom prompts with local AI providers.</strong>
Filename suggestions from LM Studio and Ollama now follow a more
reliable step-by-step flow, so custom instructions are less likely to
leak into the final name.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed confusing local AI filename failures.</strong> When a
local provider cannot return a usable filename, NameQuick now shows a
clearer problem instead of silently accepting malformed output.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
